{
  "chapter": "002",
  "title": "夏本纪",
  "translations": {
    "1": {
      "title": "禹的身世",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏禹</span>，名叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">文命</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">颛顼</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>的父亲叫<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">黄帝</span>的玄孙，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝颛顼</span>的孙子。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的曾祖父<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">昌意</span>和父亲<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>都没有登上帝位，只做<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">人臣</span>。"
    },
    "1.1": {
      "title": "鲧治水无功",
      "text": "在<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>的时候，洪水滔天，浩浩荡荡包围山陵，淹没<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襄陵</span>，下面的百姓为此忧虑。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>寻求能治水的人，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群臣</span>和<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>都说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>可以。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>违背命令破坏族规，不可用。\"<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>说：\"大家之中没有比<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>更贤能的，愿帝试用他。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>听从<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>的意见，任用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>治水。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">九年（时长）</span>过去，洪水没有平息，治水没有成功。"
    },
    "1.2": {
      "title": "舜殛鲧于羽山",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝尧</span>就另寻他人，得到了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>被提拔起用，代理<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>的政务，出巡<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>。他巡察<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>治水毫无成效，就在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羽山</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">殛</span>杀了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>。天下人都认为<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>杀是正确的。"
    },
    "1.3": {
      "title": "舜举禹继父业",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">举</span>用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>，让他继承<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>的事业。"
    },
    "2": {
      "title": "舜命禹为司空",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>后，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>问<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四岳</span>说：\"有谁能成就光大<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的事业，可以担任官职？\"大家都说：\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯禹</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">司空</span>，可以成就光大<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>的功业。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"嗯，好！\"于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">命</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"你去平治水土，一定要努力啊。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>拜谢叩头，谦让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">契</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>说：\"你还是去视察你的职事吧。\""
    },
    "2.1": {
      "title": "禹的品德",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>为人敏捷勤劳，他的品德无可指摘，他的仁爱使人亲近，他的言语值得信任；他的声音合乎音律，他的举止合乎法度，他的行事合乎称量标准；他勤勉庄重，堪为纲纪。"
    },
    "3": {
      "title": "禹治水大略",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>于是和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>一起奉行帝的命令，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">命</span>令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>和<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>征发民众分土治水，跋山立标，测定<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">高山</span>和大川。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>伤心先父<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">鲧</span>治水无功而遭<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">诛</span>戮，于是<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">劳身焦思</span>，在外<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十三年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：过门不入\">过家门不敢入（过门不入）</span>。他节省<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">衣</span>食，对<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">鬼神</span>尽<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">孝</span>敬；居住简陋的<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">宫室</span>，把费用都花在沟渠上。 - 陆地行走乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>， - 水上行走乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">船</span>， - 泥地行走乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">橇</span>， - 山地行走乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">檋</span>。 - 左手持<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">准绳</span>，右手拿<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">规矩</span>，按照<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">四时</span>行事，以此开辟<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九州</span>，疏通九条道路，修筑九个湖泽的堤防，丈量九座山岭。"
    },
    "3.1": {
      "title": "粮食调济",
      "text": "让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众庶</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">稻</span>种，可以种在低湿的地方。<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">命</span>令<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">后稷</span>给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众庶</span>难以获得的食物。粮食不够的时候，从有余的地方调剂给不足的地方，以此平衡<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>之间的物资。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>还实地考察各地适宜出产的物品作为<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">贡</span>品，以及山川的交通便利之处。"
    },
    "4": {
      "title": "冀州",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>治水从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">冀州</span>开始。 <span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">冀州</span>：完成了<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">壶口</span>的工程，治理<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁</span>山和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岐</span>山。已修治<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太原</span>，直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岳阳</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">覃怀</span>的工程已见成效，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衡漳</span>。这里的土壤为白色细土。田赋是上上等而杂有上中等，田地是中中等，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">卫</span>水已经顺流，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大陆</span>泽已经可以耕种。<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">鸟夷</span>进贡皮衣。贡品从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">碣石</span>山右侧，进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>。"
    },
    "5": {
      "title": "沇州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沇州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九河</span>已经疏通，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雷夏</span>已成为湖泽，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沮</span>水已会合入泽，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桑</span>林之土已可养蚕，于是人民得以从丘陵上下来居住平地。这里的土壤是黑色肥土，草丰盛茂密，树木高长。田地是中下等，赋税为正等，治理了<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十有三年（时长）</span>才能和其他州同样缴纳。贡品是漆和丝，竹筐里盛放织有花纹的丝织品。贡品浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漯</span>水，通达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。"
    },
    "6": {
      "title": "青州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海岱</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">青州</span>：<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">堣夷</span>地区已经治理，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">濰</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淄</span>水已经疏通。这里的土壤是白色肥土，海滨是广阔的盐碱地，田地是斥卤盐地。田地是上下等，赋税是中上等。贡品是盐和细葛布，各种海产，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岱</span>山谷地出产丝、麻、铅、松木、怪石，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">莱夷</span>可以放牧，竹筐里盛放柞蚕丝。贡品浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶</span>水，通达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>。"
    },
    "7": {
      "title": "徐州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海岱</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">徐州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沂水</span>已治理，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒙</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羽</span>山已可种植。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大野</span>已成湖泽，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东原</span>已底定平坦。这里的土壤是红色黏土，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">草</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>丛生繁茂。田地是上中等，赋税是中中等。贡品是五色土，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">羽</span>山谷地出产彩色野鸡羽毛，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">峄</span>山南面出产独生<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">桐</span>木，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>边可做磬的石头，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">淮夷</span>进贡珍珠和<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鱼</span>，竹筐里盛放黑色细绸白色丝织品。贡品浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>，通达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。"
    },
    "8": {
      "title": "扬州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮海</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">扬州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭蠡</span>已成湖泽，是候鸟栖息之地。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三江</span>已入海，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">震泽</span>已经安定。<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹箭</span>已遍布。这里的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">草</span>繁茂鲜嫩，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">木</span>高大耸立，土壤是涂泥。田地是下下等，赋税是下上等而杂有上中等。贡品是金、银、铜三种金属，美玉、次玉、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">竹箭</span>，象牙、兽皮、羽毛、旄牛尾，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">岛夷</span>进贡草布衣服，竹筐里盛放织有贝纹的织物，还有包好的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">橘</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">柚</span>作为贡品。贡品沿<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江海</span>而来，通达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>。"
    },
    "9": {
      "title": "荆州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆</span>山到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衡阳</span>是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>像诸侯朝见天子一样流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>中。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>顺畅，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沱</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涔</span>水已经疏通，云泽、梦泽已经治理。这里的土壤是涂泥。田地是下中等，赋税是上下等。贡品是羽毛、旄牛尾、象牙、兽皮，金、银、铜三种金属，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">杶</span>木、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">榦</span>木、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">栝</span>木、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">柏</span>木，磨石、细磨石、箭镞石、朱砂，箭竹、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">簬</span>竹、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">楛</span>木，这三种物产由三个诸侯国进贡，还有包裹的<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">菁茅</span>，竹筐里盛放黑红色的玉串和丝带，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>进献大<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龟</span>。贡品浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沱</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涔</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>，越过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南河</span>。"
    },
    "10": {
      "title": "豫州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆河</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">豫州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瀍</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涧</span>水都流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥</span>泽已成湖泽，疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荷泽</span>，水被及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">明都</span>。这里的土壤松软，低洼地为肥黑土。田地是中上等，赋税是上中等而杂有中等。贡品是漆、丝、细葛布、苎麻布，竹筐里盛放细丝棉絮，有时还进贡打磨钟磬的石头。贡品浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。"
    },
    "11": {
      "title": "梁州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阳</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黑水</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梁州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">嶓</span>山已经开发，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沱</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涔</span>水已经疏通，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蔡</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">蒙</span>山已经开辟道路进行祭祀，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">和夷</span>取得了治水的业绩。这里的土壤是青黑色。田地是下上等，赋税是下中等而有上下三种不同。贡品是美玉、铁、银、可刻镂的钢、箭镞石、磬石，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">熊</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">罴</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">狐</span>、<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">貍</span>的皮毛和毛布。贡品从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西倾</span>山沿桓水而来，浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">潜</span>水，越过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沔</span>水，进入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>，横渡<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。"
    },
    "12": {
      "title": "雍州",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黑水</span>和<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>之间是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雍州</span>：<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">弱水</span>已向西流，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泾水</span>流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭汭</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漆</span>水、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沮</span>水已经顺流，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沣水</span>也来汇合。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岐</span>山已经祭祀开辟，<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">终南</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敦物</span>一直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸟鼠</span>山。高原低湿之地都取得了成绩，直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">都野</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三危</span>已经开通，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">三苗</span>安居顺从。这里的土壤是黄色肥土。田地是上上等，赋税是中下等。贡品是美玉、琳玉、琅玕。贡品浮行于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">积石</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">龙门</span>的<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西河</span>，会合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭汭</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">昆仑</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">析支</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渠搜</span>进贡毛布，<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">西戎</span>部族也都安定顺从。"
    },
    "13": {
      "title": "九山脉络",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九山</span>：从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汧</span>山、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">岐</span>山到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆山</span>，越过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">壶口</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">雷首</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太岳</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砥柱</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">析城</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">王屋</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太行</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">常山</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">碣石</span>，入于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">西倾</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">硃圉</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸟鼠</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">太华</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">熊耳</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">外方</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桐柏</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">负尾</span>；疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">嶓冢</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荆山</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">内方</span>到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大别</span>；从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶山</span>南面到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">衡山</span>，过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">敷浅原</span>。"
    },
    "14": {
      "title": "疏导九川",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九川</span>："
    },
    "14.1": {
      "title": "弱水",
      "text": "<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">弱水</span>流到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">合黎</span>，余波流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">流沙</span>。"
    },
    "14.2": {
      "title": "黑水",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黑水</span>，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三危</span>，流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">南海</span>。"
    },
    "14.3": {
      "title": "河水",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">积石</span>起，到达<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">龙门</span>，南到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">华阴</span>，东到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">砥柱</span>，又东到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">盟津</span>，东过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛汭</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大邳</span>，北过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">降水</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大陆</span>，北面分流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九河</span>，合流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">逆河</span>，入于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>。"
    },
    "14.4": {
      "title": "汉水",
      "text": "从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">嶓冢</span>疏通瀁水，东流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汉水</span>，又东流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">苍浪之水</span>，过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">三澨</span>，流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">大别</span>，南流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>，东汇为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">彭蠡</span>泽，东流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">北江</span>，入于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>。"
    },
    "14.5": {
      "title": "江水",
      "text": "从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶山</span>疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">长江</span>，东边分流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沱</span>，又东到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">醴</span>，过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九江</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">东陵</span>，向东斜北汇合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汇</span>泽，东流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中江</span>，入于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">梅</span>。"
    },
    "14.6": {
      "title": "济水",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沇水</span>，东流为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">济水</span>，流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>，溢出为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荥</span>泽，东出<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">陶丘</span>北面，又东到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">荷</span>泽，又东北汇合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">汶</span>水，又东北入于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>。"
    },
    "14.7": {
      "title": "淮水",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">淮河</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">桐柏</span>开始，东汇合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泗水</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沂水</span>，东入于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>。"
    },
    "14.8": {
      "title": "渭水",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">渭水</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸟鼠同穴</span>开始，东汇合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沣</span>，又东北到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">泾水</span>，东过<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">漆</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">沮</span>，流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。"
    },
    "14.9": {
      "title": "雒水",
      "text": "疏通<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛水</span>从<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">熊耳</span>开始，东北汇合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">涧</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">瀍</span>，又东汇合于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">伊</span>，东北流入<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">黄河</span>。"
    },
    "15": {
      "title": "九州既同",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">九州</span>统一，四方边境都可居住，九山开通，九川疏通源头，九泽都筑起了堤坝，四海汇合共同归向。<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六府</span>都治理得很好，各地土壤得到正当评定，谨慎征收财赋，都按<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三壤</span>的等级制定赋税。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">中国</span>赐给土地和姓氏：\"恭敬地把德行放在首位，不要违背我的<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">行</span>为。\""
    },
    "15.1": {
      "title": "甸服",
      "text": "令<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之国以外<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">甸服</span>：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>内交纳带穗的整禾，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百里</span>内交纳禾穗，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百里</span>内交纳去秆的禾，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">四百里</span>内交纳粟，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>内交纳米。"
    },
    "15.2": {
      "title": "侯服",
      "text": "<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">甸服</span>以外<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">侯服</span>：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">百里</span>内是采邑，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百里</span>内是卿大夫的任国，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百里</span>内是<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>。"
    },
    "15.3": {
      "title": "绥服",
      "text": "<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">侯服</span>以外<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">绥服</span>：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百里</span>内推行文教，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百里</span>内奋力武卫。"
    },
    "15.4": {
      "title": "要服",
      "text": "<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">绥服</span>以外<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">要服</span>：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百里</span>内是夷人之地，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百里</span>内是流放犯人之地。"
    },
    "15.5": {
      "title": "荒服",
      "text": "<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">要服</span>以外<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五百里</span>为<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">荒服</span>：<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">三百里</span>内是蛮人之地，<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">二百里</span>内是流放重犯之地。"
    },
    "16": {
      "title": "告成功于天下",
      "text": "东面直到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">海</span>边，西面被及<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">流沙</span>，北方、南方都是如此：<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">声教讫于四海</span>。于是帝赐给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span><span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玄圭</span>，用来向天下<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">告成功</span>。天下从此太平安定。"
    },
    "17": {
      "title": "皋陶述谋",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>担任<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">士</span>以<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">理</span>治理民众。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>临朝，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">伯夷</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>一起在帝前议论。"
    },
    "17.1": {
      "title": "信道德",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>陈述他的谋略说：\"真诚地遵守<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">道德</span>，谋划就会明达，辅政就能和谐。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"对，具体怎么做？\""
    },
    "17.2": {
      "title": "慎其身修",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>说：\"啊！要谨慎修养自身，考虑长远，使九族和睦有序，众多贤明的人辅佐，近处做好，远处的事就能做到。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>拜谢他的美言，说：\"是的。\""
    },
    "17.3": {
      "title": "知人安民",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>说：\"啊！关键在于知人善任，在于安抚民众。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"咳！都像这样的话，连帝都觉得很难啊。<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">知人则智</span>，就能任用合适的官员；能安抚百姓就是仁惠，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份·规范：黎民\">百姓（黎民）</span>就会怀念他。能知人善任又能仁惠，还担心什么<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">驩兜</span>，还用迁徙什么<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">有苗</span>，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：巧言令色\">何畏乎巧言善色佞人（巧言令色）</span>？\""
    },
    "17.4": {
      "title": "九德",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>说：\"对，啊！人的行为有<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">九德</span>，也可说他有美德。\"于是说：\"从开始做事起，宽厚而庄严，温柔而有主见，忠厚而恭敬，能治理而谨慎，驯顺而刚毅，正直而温和，简易而廉洁，刚强而朴实，刚健而合义。彰显他的常德，就是吉祥。每天阐明<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三德</span>，日夜恭敬地辅助治家；每天严肃恭敬地践行<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六德</span>，明察国事。普遍接受广施恩德，<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">九德</span>都得到推行，俊杰之人居于官位，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百吏</span>恭敬谨慎。不要教人邪佞淫乱和诡诈之术。不是合适的人居官位，就叫扰乱天事。<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">天讨</span>有罪之人，<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">五刑</span>有五种用法。我的话是否可以施行？\""
    },
    "17.5": {
      "title": "禹赞皋陶言",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"你的话确实可以成就事功。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>说：\"我没有多少见识，只是想赞助治道罢了。\""
    },
    "17.6": {
      "title": "舜命禹言",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>对<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"你也说些好言论吧。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>拜谢说：\"啊，我说什么呢！我每天只是想着孜孜不倦地做事。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>诘问<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"什么叫孜孜不倦？\""
    },
    "17.7": {
      "title": "禹述治水",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"洪水滔天，浩浩荡荡包围山陵，淹没<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">襄陵</span>，下民都沉溺于洪水中。我陆行乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">车</span>，水行乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>，泥行乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">橇</span>，山行乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">檋</span>，跋山伐木立标。和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>一起给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众庶</span><span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">稻</span>米和鲜食。疏通九川到达四海，疏浚田间小沟大沟使水入河。和<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">稷</span>一起给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众庶</span>难得的食物。粮食少的时候，从有余的地方调给不足的地方，让人民迁徙就地居住。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">众民</span>于是安定，万国得到治理。\"<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>说：\"对，这真是你的美好功业。\""
    },
    "17.8": {
      "title": "禹劝舜慎位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"啊，帝！要谨慎您在位的职责，安守您的本分。辅助德治，天下就会大为响应。以清洁的心意昭然等待<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">上帝</span>的命令，天会再次降命以福佑。\""
    },
    "17.9": {
      "title": "舜论辅臣",
      "text": "帝说：\"唉，臣下啊，臣下啊！<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语·现代：股肱之臣\">臣作朕股肱耳目（股肱之臣）</span>。我想左右抚养民众，你们辅助我。我想观察古人的服章徽志。<span class=\"astronomy\" title=\"天文\">日月星辰</span>，要绘制<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">文绣</span>和<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">服色</span>，你们要明晰之。我想听<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">六律</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五声</span><span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">八音</span>，来察治乱，以辨别五言，你们要谛听。我有过失之时，你们要匡正辅助我。你们不要当面奉承，背后诽谤我。要敬重<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">四辅臣</span>。至于众多<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">谗嬖臣</span>，君德真诚施行，他们就都会清除。\""
    },
    "17.10": {
      "title": "禹应答",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"是。帝若不按时节行事，善恶不分混同，就不会有功效。\""
    },
    "17.11": {
      "title": "舜戒丹朱之傲",
      "text": "帝说：\"不要像<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">丹硃</span>那样傲慢，只好慢游嬉戏，没有水也要行<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">舟</span>，成群淫乱于家中，以致断绝了世系。我不能顺从这种行为。\""
    },
    "17.12": {
      "title": "禹自述功业",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>说：\"我娶了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">涂山氏</span>的女子，癸日、甲日结婚，生下<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>我都不把他当儿子看待，因此才能完成水土之功。辅成<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">五服</span>，直到<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五千里</span>，每州用<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">十二</span>师，外至四海，都建立了<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>个长官，各有成功之道。只有<span class=\"tribe\" title=\"族群\">苗</span>民顽固不肯就功业，帝要考虑这个问题。\"帝说：\"推行我的德政，是你的功劳使事业有条不紊。\""
    },
    "17.13": {
      "title": "皋陶推崇禹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>于是敬重<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的德行，命令民众都效法<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>。不照话做的，就施以刑罚。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的德行大为彰明。"
    },
    "18": {
      "title": "夔作乐",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夔</span><span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">行</span>乐，祖宗神灵降临，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">群后</span>相互谦让，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">鸟兽</span>翔集起舞，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">箫韶</span>演奏<span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>章之后，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">凤皇</span>飞来仪容端庄，<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">百兽</span>都随着起舞，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百官</span>和睦融洽。"
    },
    "18.1": {
      "title": "帝作歌",
      "text": "帝因此作歌说：\"承受上天的旨命，要依循时令、谨慎细致。\"于是唱道：\"股肱之臣欢喜啊，元首振兴起来啊，<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">百工</span>兴盛啊！\""
    },
    "18.2": {
      "title": "皋陶答歌",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>拜手叩头高声说：\"要想啊！率领大家兴办事业，要谨慎你的法度，恭敬啊！\"于是又作歌说：\"元首明达啊，股肱贤良啊，众事安康啊！\"又唱道：\"元首琐碎啊，股肱懈怠啊，万事败坏啊！\""
    },
    "18.3": {
      "title": "帝拜受",
      "text": "帝拜谢说：\"对啊，去努力做吧！\"于是天下都尊奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>明察度数和声乐，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>成为山川神主。"
    },
    "19": {
      "title": "舜荐禹",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span>向天<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">荐</span>举<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>，作为继承人。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十七年（时长）</span>后<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝舜</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>守丧完毕，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>避让<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">舜</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商均</span>，隐居到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">阳城</span>。"
    },
    "19.1": {
      "title": "禹即天子位",
      "text": "天下<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都离开<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">商均</span>去<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>于是就登上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之位，南面朝见天下，国号叫<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏后</span>，姓<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姒氏</span>。"
    },
    "20": {
      "title": "禹举皋陶与益",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝禹</span>即位后，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">举</span>荐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>，打算把政权授给他，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">卒</span>。于是<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">封</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">皋陶</span>的后代于<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">英</span>、<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">六</span>，也有在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">许</span>的。然后又<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">举</span>用<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>，把政事委任给他。"
    },
    "21": {
      "title": "禹崩于会稽",
      "text": "<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">十年（时长）</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝禹</span>东出<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">巡狩</span>，到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>就<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>了。把<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">天下</span>授予<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>。<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间·规范：时长\">三年（时长）</span>守丧完毕，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>把帝位让给<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝禹</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>，自己避居在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">箕山</span>南面。"
    },
    "21.1": {
      "title": "启即天子位",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>贤能，天下人都归心于他。等<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>后，虽然把帝位授给了<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>，但<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>辅佐<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的时日尚浅，天下还没有归顺。所以<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都离开<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">益</span>去<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">朝</span>见<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>，说：\"我的君主是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝禹</span>的儿子啊。\"于是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>就登上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之位，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏后帝启</span>。"
    },
    "22": {
      "title": "启的母亲",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏后帝启</span>，是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>的儿子，他的母亲是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">涂山氏</span>的女儿。"
    },
    "23": {
      "title": "甘之誓",
      "text": "<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有扈氏</span>不服，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>讨他，双方在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">甘</span>大战。将要开战之前，作<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">甘誓</span>，于是召集<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">六卿</span>向他们申明。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">启</span>说：\"啊！<span class=\"official\" title=\"官职\">六事</span>之人，我发誓告诉你们：<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有扈氏</span>轻侮<span class=\"concept\" title=\"思想\">五行</span>，懈怠废弃<span class=\"institution\" title=\"名物\">三正</span>，上天因此要断绝他的天命。如今我只是恭敬地<span class=\"ritual\" title=\"礼仪\">行</span>使上天的惩罚。左边不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>在左的敌人，右边不<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">攻</span>在右的敌人，你们就是不遵从命令。驾御不能驱策好<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">马</span>，你们就是不遵从命令。听从命令的，在祖庙赏赐；不听从命令的，在社坛<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">僇</span>杀，我还会把你们的妻子儿女一起<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">僇</span>杀。\""
    },
    "23.1": {
      "title": "灭有扈",
      "text": "于是<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">灭</span>了<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有扈氏</span>。天下都来朝见。"
    },
    "24": {
      "title": "太康失国",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏后帝启</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太康</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝太康</span>丧失了国家，他的五个弟兄，在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">洛汭</span>等待他，作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">五子之歌</span>。"
    },
    "25": {
      "title": "中康立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太康</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中康</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中康</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝中康</span>的时候，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羲</span>氏、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">和</span>氏沉湎酒色，荒废时令，扰乱了日序。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">胤</span>前去征讨他们，作了<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">胤征</span>。"
    },
    "26": {
      "title": "夏王世系",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">中康</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝相</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝相</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝少康</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝少康</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝予</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝予</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝槐</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝槐</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝芒</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝芒</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝泄</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝泄</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝不降</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝不降</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，弟弟<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝扃</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝扃</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝廑</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。"
    },
    "26.1": {
      "title": "孔甲立",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝廑</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span><span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝不降</span>的儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝孔甲</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝孔甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>位后，好祭方术<span class=\"mythical\" title=\"神话\">鬼神</span>之事，行为淫乱。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">夏后氏</span>的德行衰落，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>背叛他。"
    },
    "26.2": {
      "title": "豢龙刘累",
      "text": "天降下两条<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>，有雌有雄，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>不能饲养，找不到<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">豢龙氏</span>。<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">陶唐</span>氏已经衰落，其后代中有<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘累</span>，曾向<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">豢龙氏</span>学习驯<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>，用来侍奉<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>赐他姓叫<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">御龙氏</span>，接受<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">豕韦</span>的后代封地。一条雌<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>死了，他把它的肉给<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夏后</span>吃。<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">夏后</span>派人来索要龙肉，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">刘累</span>害怕就迁居离开了。"
    },
    "27": {
      "title": "桀亡夏兴商",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝皋</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝皋</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝发</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝发</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">崩</span>，儿子<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝履癸</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">立</span>，这就是<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝桀</span>的时候，从<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>以来<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>大多背叛夏，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>不致力于德政，反以武力<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">伤</span>害<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">百姓</span>无法忍受。于是召来<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>把他<span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">囚</span>禁在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夏台</span>，不久又释放了他。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>修明德政，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>都归附<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>就率领军队去<span class=\"verb-military\" title=\"军事动词\">伐</span>讨<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">夏桀</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>逃到<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸣条</span>，于是被<span class=\"legal\" title=\"刑法\">放</span>逐而死。 - <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">桀</span>对人说：\"我后悔没有在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">夏台</span><span class=\"verb-penalty\" title=\"刑罚动词\">杀</span>死<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>，使事情到了这个地步。\" <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>于是登上<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">天子</span>之位，代替<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>朝统治天下。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">汤</span>分封<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>的后代，到<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">周</span>时封在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">杞</span>。"
    },
    "28": {
      "title": "太史公曰",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太史公</span>说：<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>是<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">姒姓</span>，他的后代分封，以国名为姓，所以有<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">夏后氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有扈氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有男氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">斟寻氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">彤城氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">襃氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">费氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">杞氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">缯氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">辛氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">冥氏</span>、<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">斟戈氏</span>。<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔子</span>厘正<span class=\"time\" title=\"时间\">夏时</span>，学者多传习<span class=\"book\" title=\"典籍\">夏小正</span>一书。从<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">虞</span>、<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏</span>时起，<span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">贡</span>赋制度就齐备了。有人说<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>在<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">江南</span>会合<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">诸侯</span>，评议功劳而○崩，就葬在那里，命名为<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>。<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">会稽</span>，就是会计的意思。"
    },
    "29": {
      "title": "赞",
      "text": "<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">尧</span>遭遇洪水，<span class=\"identity\" title=\"身份\">黎人</span>被阻困饥。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">禹</span>勤修沟渠，<span class=\"idiom\" title=\"成语\">手足胼胝</span>。 据说乘<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">四载</span>出行，行动依循<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">四时</span>。 娶妻有日，过家门而不入私。 <span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">九</span>州土地治理，<span class=\"artifact\" title=\"器物\">玄圭</span>被赐予。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">帝启</span><span class=\"verb-political\" title=\"政治动词\">嗣立</span>，<span class=\"dynasty\" title=\"氏族\">有扈</span>违抗王命。 <span class=\"quantity\" title=\"数量\">五</span>子作歌，<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">太康</span>丧失政权。 <span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">羿</span>、<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">浞</span>这样的人欺凌君主，<span class=\"feudal-state\" title=\"邦国\">夏室</span>不振。 降及<span class=\"person\" title=\"人名\">孔甲</span>，扰<span class=\"biology\" title=\"生物\">龙</span>违背其性。 可叹那<span class=\"place\" title=\"地名\">鸣条</span>之地，夏桀的下场真是不吉！"
    }
  }
}